Text: Intersect Capital LLC Raises Position in iShares Select Dividend ETF (NASDAQ:DVY) Intersect Capital LLC increased its holdings in shares of iShares Select Dividend ETF (NASDAQ:DVY) by 51.0% during the 2nd quarter, according to its most recent filing with the Securities and Exchange Commission. The firm owned 6,422 shares of the company's stock after buying an additional 2,170 shares during the quarter.
